<div class="entryuserpic"><img src="http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/93571119/874250" title="" alt=""height="100" width="100"  /></div></div>

<div class="entrycontent">If your raid array is using a hardware controller then it'll show up as a regular single SCSI or IDE device, and will work.  If it's software raid, I would expect it to be OS specific and not work.<br /><br />I have only ever had custom built machines.<br /><br />Photoshop might be a good reason not to use Linux.  How many years has it been since you tried Gimp?</div>

